definition: to come and go/to have dealings with/to be in relation with
to come/to arrive/to come round/ever since/next
old variant of 往[wang3]
to go (in a direction)/to/towards/(of a train) bound for/past/previous

sentences.english: A girl in Yao minority dress warmly greeting customers.
sentences.chinese: 穿着民族服装的瑶家姑娘，热情地招呼来往市民。

sentences.english: We had been doing business with each other for years before we quarrelled.
sentences.chinese: 在吵翻之前，我们多年来在业务上一直来往。

sentences.english: We sat down on the park bench and watched the people as they passed.
sentences.chinese: 我们坐在公园的长凳上，把稳考察着来往的行人。

sentences.english: The clamour of the heavy traffic gave you a headache.
sentences.chinese: 来往车辆嘈杂的声浪使人头痛。

sentences.english: He insinuated his cat through traffic.
sentences.chinese: 他驾车慢慢地行进于来往车辆中。

sentences.english: Hanhan's neighbor, usually didn't socialize much and scholar.
sentences.chinese: 憨憨与秀才是邻居，平时来往不多。

sentences.english: No respectable citizen in town had anything to do with Mad Henry
sentences.chinese: 市镇里没有哪个正派人与其有任何来往。

sentences.english: He has learned English for only one year, yet he can communicate with people in English.
sentences.chinese: 他才教一年英文，但未能用英文与己来往了。

sentences.english: Although China and Saudi is thousands of kilometers away, the people in both countries have intercourse since long ago.
sentences.chinese: 中国和沙特虽相距数千公里，但两国人民早有来往。

sentences.english: Watch out for cars when you cross the street.
sentences.chinese: 过街时要注意来往车辆。

sentences.english: Deal with all correspondences of department.
sentences.chinese: 处理部门全部来往通信。

sentences.english: Description: Operates flights between Hong Kong and destinations in Mainland China.
sentences.chinese: 营运来往香港及中国内地航点的航班。

sentences.english: Big anniversaries come and go, but moments like this arise only rarely.
sentences.chinese: 大型年度庆典来来往往，但像这样的时刻很出现。

sentences.english: The port is crowded with ships coming and going.
sentences.chinese: 港口一片繁忙景象，来往船只风樯林立。

sentences.english: Traveling time among the three cities will be shortened to 15 to 20 minutes.
sentences.chinese: 来往三市之间的时间将缩短到15至20分钟。

sentences.english: A record of financial transactions kept in a ledger.
sentences.chinese: 在分成类帐中保存的财务来往记录。
